            "answer_text": "If you're laying out photos and want text under each of them, I'd suggest making an unordered list, and inserting into each list item element the picture and a paragraph text. So it'd look like this: <ul><li><img src=\"beginnermensimage.jpg\"><p>Beginner mens image</p></li><li><img src=\"advancedmensimage.jpg\"><p>Advanced mens image</p></li></ul> It should automatically put the text below. Thanks ",
